How many years ago was that?

126
00:07:20,375 --> 00:07:21,791
How should I know?

127
00:07:21,875 --> 00:07:24,666
That was a really long time
ago before I was even born.

128
00:07:24,750 --> 00:07:27,375
Look, what's Ken
doing over there?

129
00:07:27,458 --> 00:07:29,208
He's relying on
that stupid book!

130
00:07:29,291 --> 00:07:31,208
So what should I do now?

131
00:07:31,291 --> 00:07:32,708
In unexpected
situations you have

132
00:07:32,791 --> 00:07:34,208
to make the
appropriate decisions.

133
00:07:34,291 --> 00:07:36,291
Let's say the restaurant you
wanna go to is closed down.

134
00:07:36,375 --> 00:07:37,916
If you're a smart guy,
then you've explored

135
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:40,333
the area for other
places to eat nearby.

136
00:07:41,416 --> 00:07:44,250
Don't worry, I'll be your
guide to the power of love.

137
00:07:46,750 --> 00:07:47,083
Sora?

138
00:07:47,791 --> 00:07:48,625
Sora?

139
00:07:48,708 --> 00:07:49,500
Sora!

140
00:07:49,583 --> 00:07:50,625
Sora!

141
00:07:50,708 --> 00:07:51,750
Sora!

142
00:07:51,833 --> 00:07:53,458
Maybe we expected
too much from him...

143
00:07:53,541 --> 00:07:54,750
Ken!

144
