There's a hot
dog stand over here.

145
00:07:59,625 --> 00:08:01,583
I guess hot dogs will do.

146
00:08:01,958 --> 00:08:04,958
I don't see a terrace, but we've
got a great view of the ocean.

147
00:08:05,041 --> 00:08:06,583
Sounds good!

148
00:08:11,166 --> 00:08:12,458
This is yummy!

149
00:08:12,541 --> 00:08:15,458
Hanging outside when the
weather's nice is the best!

150
00:08:15,541 --> 00:08:18,291
Thank you so much for
inviting me to lunch Ken.

151
00:08:18,625 --> 00:08:20,375
No problem, you're welcome!

152
00:08:20,458 --> 00:08:23,083
Wait a minute, why is she
