better off just staying dreams.

187
00:09:51,791 --> 00:09:53,541
Mr. Policeman...

188
00:09:53,625 --> 00:09:56,541
"Dreams are better off
just staying dreams"?

189
00:09:56,625 --> 00:09:57,833
No way!

190
00:09:57,916 --> 00:10:00,208
Our dreams are goals that
we can make happen!

191
00:10:00,291 --> 00:10:03,250
We do whatever we can
to make them reality.

192
00:10:03,958 --> 00:10:05,500
Mr. Policeman?

193
00:10:05,583 --> 00:10:07,083
Yeah?

194
00:10:07,166 --> 00:10:08,625
Come on Mr. Policeman.

195
00:10:08,708 --> 00:10:10,541
Let's make your dream come true!

196
00:10:10,625 --> 00:10:12,000
Sora.

197
00:10:12,083 --> 00:10:13,666
Well, let's go!

198
00:10:13,750 --> 00:10:14,875
Yeah!

199
00:10:15,541 --> 00:10:17,375
