206
00:10:30,125 --> 00:10:32,041
Come on, don't be so
pessimistic, your chance will

207
00:10:32,125 --> 00:10:33,750
definitely come,
you've just gotta believe!

208
00:10:33,833 --> 00:10:35,125
Right, I just gotta believe!

209
00:10:35,208 --> 00:10:37,041
Just like she said, I can't
lose heart and give up.

210
00:10:37,125 --> 00:10:39,250
I gotta believe that
my chance will come!

211
00:10:39,791 --> 00:10:40,500
Look!

212
00:10:40,583 --> 00:10:42,125
Isn't that Miss Kate?

213
00:10:44,500 --> 00:10:45,708
Hi, how're you doing Kate?

214
00:10:45,791 --> 00:10:47,500
Were you waiting long Robert?

215
00:10:49,916 --> 00:10:52,708
