no chance of winning.

216
00:10:52,791 --> 00:10:54,166
That's not true!

217
00:10:54,250 --> 00:10:56,125
Women don't just care about
looks or brains or money,

218
00:10:56,208 --> 00:10:58,458
they like a man that's
warm and sincere too.

219
00:10:58,541 --> 00:11:00,333
