a great guy you are,

220
00:11:00,416 --> 00:11:02,500
she thinks you're a great catch!

221
00:11:02,583 --> 00:11:05,125
Okay, I'm gonna go
find out what's going on.

222
00:11:05,625 --> 00:11:08,791
Hey Sora, what do
you mean by 'find out'?

223
